{"tid":894273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲女遇電騙 被呃19萬","createTime":"2018-11-08T09:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T11:33:34.000Z","uid":28435,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e79c9b8e49117b95765e639d9ba4bb04cf92b6ab","tid":894273,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"早上8時許，警方接獲一名18歲少女報案，指她早前接獲一名不明男子來電，對方自稱為執法人員，並指她涉及一宗刑事案件，要求她匯款至一個內地戶口。女事主不虞有詐，遂按該名男子指示匯款約19萬元，但其後與該名男子失去聯絡，始覺受騙。警方經初步調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"7545ce89d25e39a94eea86d2425b03480baba819","tid":894273,"uid":84926,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"18歲女19萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d98d0f70241ca95654a28c89a10e9e56884975","tid":894273,"uid":192158,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:13:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bf75272e8def2286d7dae16397a8ba33dd6941b","tid":894273,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"依家啲人唔睇新聞㗎？"},{"pid":"eff00b9ef87282e42dcea8a063d2a2597db65b73","tid":894273,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"一係就有錢女 一係就本身都黑錢黎"},{"pid":"106fc866e465c9b702cf34c5cf46cd265f7fc20f","tid":894273,"uid":68489,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:34:17.000Z","msg":"真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n啲辛苦錢冇曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4181dd4e57290c64864e4c525b04135920ad8deb","tid":894273,"uid":19712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9bf75272e8def2286d7dae16397a8ba33dd6941b","tid":894273,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:19:40.000Z","